<lb n="0779a23"/>
<lb n="0779a24"/><head type="no">No. 685 [No. 686]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0779a25"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title>佛說盂蘭盆經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0779a26"/>
<lb n="0779a27"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0779005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔西〕－【宋】</note><app n="0779005"><lem>西</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>晉<note n="0779006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">月氏三藏＝三藏法師【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月氏三藏＝三藏法師【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779006"><lem>月氏三藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">三藏法師</rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb n="0779a28"/><p>聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。大
<lb n="0779a29"/>目<note n="0779007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乾＝犍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乾＝犍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779007"><lem>乾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">犍</rdg></app>連始得六通。欲度父母報乳哺之恩。即
<pb ed="T" id="T16.0685.0779b" n="0779b"/>
<lb n="0779b01"/>以道眼觀視世間。見其亡母生餓鬼中。不見
<lb n="0779b02"/>飲食皮骨連<note n="0779008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">立＝柱【宮】</note><app n="0779008"><lem>立</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">柱</rdg></app>。目連悲哀。<note n="0779009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＋（以）【三】</note><note n="0779009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即＋（以）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779009"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">即以</rdg></app>&CB00425;盛飯往餉
<lb n="0779b03"/>其母。母得&CB00425;飯。便以左手障<note n="0779010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＝&CB00425;【三】</note><note n="0779010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯＝&CB00425;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779010"><lem>飯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00425;</rdg></app>右手摶<note n="0779011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＝食【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯＝食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779011"><lem>飯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">食</rdg></app>
<lb n="0779b04"/>食未入口化成火炭。遂不得食。目連大叫悲
<lb n="0779b05"/>號<note n="0779012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">啼＝涕【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">啼＝涕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779012"><lem>啼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">涕</rdg></app>泣。馳還白佛。具陳如此</p>
<lb n="0779b06"/><p>佛言。汝母罪根深結。非汝一人力所奈何。汝
<lb n="0779b07"/>雖孝順聲動天地。天神地<note n="0779013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">神＝祈【宋】，祇【元】【明】</note><note n="0779013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神＝祈【宋】，＝祇【元】【明】</note><app n="0779013"><lem>神</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">祈</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">祇</rdg></app>邪魔外道。道
<lb n="0779b08"/>士四天王神。亦不能奈何。當須十方眾僧威
<lb n="0779b09"/>神之力。乃得解脫</p>
<lb n="0779b10"/><p>吾今當<note n="0779014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為汝〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔為汝〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779014"><lem>為汝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>說救濟之法。令一切難皆離憂
<lb n="0779b11"/>苦<note n="0779015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔罪障消除〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔罪障消除〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779015"><lem>罪障消除</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0779b12"/><p>佛告目蓮。十方眾僧<note n="0779016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔於〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779016"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>七月十五日僧自恣
<lb n="0779b13"/>時。當為七世父母。及現在父母厄難中者。具
<lb n="0779b14"/>飯百味五果汲灌盆器。香油<note n="0779017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">錠&CB02536;＝挻燭【宋】，鋋燭【元】【明】【宮】</note><note n="0779017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">錠&CB02536;＝挻燭【宋】，＝鋋燭【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779017"><lem>錠&CB02536;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">挻燭</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">鋋燭</rdg></app>床敷臥具。
<lb n="0779b15"/>盡世甘美以著盆中。供養十方大德眾僧。當
<lb n="0779b16"/>此之日。一切聖眾或在山間禪定<note n="0779018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔或〕－【宮】</note><app n="0779018"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>得四道
<lb n="0779b17"/>果。<note n="0779019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＋（在）【元】【明】</note><app n="0779019"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">或在</rdg></app>樹下經行。或六通自在教化聲聞緣
<lb n="0779b18"/>覺。或十地菩薩大人權現比丘。在大眾中皆
<lb n="0779b19"/>同一心受&CB00425;和羅飯。具清淨戒聖眾之道其
<lb n="0779b20"/>德汪洋。其有供養此等自恣僧者。現<note n="0779020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝世【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在＝世【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779020"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">世</rdg></app>父
<lb n="0779b21"/>母<note n="0779021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔七世父母〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0779021"><lem>七世父母</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0779022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">六種親屬＝六親眷屬【三】</note><note n="0779022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">六種親屬＝六親眷屬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779022"><lem>六種親屬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">六親眷屬</rdg></app>。得出三途之苦。應
<lb n="0779b22"/>時解脫衣食自然。若<note n="0779023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復有人〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔復有人〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779023"><lem>復有人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>父母現在者福
<lb n="0779b23"/>樂百年。若<note n="0779024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔已亡〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔已亡〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779024"><lem>已亡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>七世父母生天。自在化生入
<lb n="0779b24"/>天華光。<note n="0779025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔受無量快樂〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔受無量快樂〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779025"><lem>受無量快樂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>時佛&CB00330;十方眾僧。皆
<lb n="0779b25"/><note n="0779026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔先〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0779026"><lem>先</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>為施主<note n="0779027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔家〕－【宮】</note><app n="0779027"><lem>家</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00057;願。<note n="0779028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（願）＋七【三】</note><note n="0779028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（願）＋七【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779028"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">願七</rdg></app>世父母。行禪定意然
<lb n="0779b26"/>後受食。初受<note n="0779029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盆＝食【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盆＝食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779029"><lem>盆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">食</rdg></app>時。先安在佛<note n="0779030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">塔＝前塔寺中佛【三】</note><note n="0779030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">塔＝前塔寺中佛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779030"><lem>塔</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">前塔寺中佛</rdg></app>前。眾僧&CB00057;
<lb n="0779b27"/>願竟。便自受食</p>
<lb n="0779b28"/><p><note n="0779031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔爾〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0779031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔爾〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0779031"><lem>爾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>時目連比丘及<note n="0779032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔此大會〕－【三】，此大會＝此大眾【宮】</note><note n="0779032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔此大會〕－【宋】【元】【明】，此大會＝此大眾【宮】</note><app n="0779032"><lem>此大會</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">此大眾</rdg></app>大菩薩眾。皆大
<lb n="0779b29"/>歡喜。<note n="0779033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔而〕－【三】</note><note n="0779033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔而〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779033"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>目連悲啼泣聲釋然除滅。<note n="0779034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【元】</note><app n="0779034"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>時目
<pb ed="T" id="T16.0685.0779c" n="0779c"/>
<lb n="0779c01"/>連<note n="0779035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其〕－【三】</note><note n="0779035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔其〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779035"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>母。即於是日得脫一劫餓鬼之苦</p>
<lb n="0779c02"/><p><note n="0779036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔爾時〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔爾時〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779036"><lem>爾時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>目連復白佛言。弟子所生<note n="0779037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔父〕－【三】</note><note n="0779037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔父〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779037"><lem>父</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>母。得蒙
<lb n="0779c03"/>三寶功德之力。眾僧威神之力故。若未來世
<lb n="0779c04"/>一切佛弟子。<note n="0779038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔行孝順者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔行孝順者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779038"><lem>行孝順者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0779039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亦應＝應亦【宋】</note><app n="0779039"><lem>亦應</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">應亦</rdg></app>奉<note n="0779040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔此〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔此〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779040"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>盂蘭盆。
<lb n="0779c05"/>救度現在父母乃至七世父母。為可爾<note n="0779041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝否【三】</note><note n="0779041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＝否【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779041"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">否</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0779c06"/><p>佛言。大善快問。我正欲說。汝今復問。善男
<lb n="0779c07"/>子。若<note n="0779042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【明】</note><app n="0779042"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>比丘比丘尼。國王太子<note n="0779043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王子〕－【三】</note><note n="0779043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔王子〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779043"><lem>王子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>大臣
<lb n="0779c08"/>宰相。三公百官萬民庶人。行<note n="0779044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">孝慈＝慈孝【三】</note><note n="0779044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">孝慈＝慈孝【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779044"><lem>孝慈</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">慈孝</rdg></app>者。皆<note n="0779045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">應＋（先）【三】</note><note n="0779045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">應＋（先）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779045"><lem>應</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">應先</rdg></app>
<lb n="0779c09"/>為所生現在父母。過去七世父母。於七月十
<lb n="0779c10"/>五日。佛歡喜日。僧自恣日。以百味<note n="0779046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飲＝飯【元】</note><app n="0779046"><lem>飲</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">飯</rdg></app>食安
<lb n="0779c11"/>盂蘭盆中。施十方自恣僧。<note n="0779047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乞〕－【三】</note><note n="0779047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔乞〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779047"><lem>乞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>願<note n="0779048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔便〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔便〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779048"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>使現在
<lb n="0779c12"/>父母壽命百年無病。無一切苦惱之患。乃至
<lb n="0779c13"/>七世父母離餓鬼苦。<note n="0779049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔得〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔得〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779049"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>生<note n="0779050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天人＝人天【三】</note><note n="0779050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天人＝人天【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779050"><lem>天人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">人天</rdg></app>中<note n="0779051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">福＝富【元】</note><app n="0779051"><lem>福</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">富</rdg></app>樂無
<lb n="0779c14"/>極</p>
<lb n="0779c15"/><p><note n="0779052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛告…人〕九字－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛告…人〕九字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779052" word-count="9"><lem>佛告諸善男子善女人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>是佛弟子修孝順者。
<lb n="0779c16"/>應念念中常憶父母<note n="0779053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔供養〕－【三】</note><note n="0779053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔供養〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779053"><lem>供養</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>乃至七世父母。年
<lb n="0779c17"/>年七月十五日。<note n="0779054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＝當【三】</note><note n="0779054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常＝當【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779054"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">當</rdg></app>以孝<note n="0779055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔順〕－【三】</note><note n="0779055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔順〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779055"><lem>順</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>慈憶所生父母。
<lb n="0779c18"/><note n="0779056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乃至七世父母〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0779056"><lem>乃至七世父母</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>為作盂蘭盆施佛及僧。以報
<lb n="0779c19"/>父母長養慈愛之恩。若一切佛弟子。應當奉
<lb n="0779c20"/>持是法</p>
<lb n="0779c21"/><p><anchor id="fxT16p0779c01"/>爾時目連比丘。四輩弟子。<note n="0779057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔聞佛所說〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔聞佛所說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779057"><lem>聞佛所說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>歡喜
<lb n="0779c22"/>奉行</p>
